overview.en: Based on the design principle of blockchain technology and decentralized anonymity, EBC has built an independent internet on distributed nodes for all the public to use, creating a decentralized e-commerce financial system.
overview.zh: EBC基于区块链技术以非中心化匿名为设计原则，在分布式节点上构建了一个独立互联网，供所有公众使用，打造去中心化电商金融体系。
